_:N230774a6ea1e406891be9fbe38063c0b <http://schema.org/description> "The National Forest Company leads the creation of The National Forest, a new, forested landscape and destination across 200 square miles of central England. Forest cover (woods and other habitats) has trebled to almost 20% and alongside a transformed environment the economic and social well-being of the area continue to grow. NFC works with the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ." .
